#### [Brawl erupts among unruly parents during 6th grade boys basketball game](https://www.foxnews.com/video/6387738984112)

Multiple parents were caught on camera breaking out into a fight after a mom approached another at an elementary kids basketball game at St. Teresa-St. Rita STREAM Academy in New York on Dec. 20. (Credit: Silive)

